{
  "texts": [
    "The latter two components are governed by the surrogate user's decisions, and conclude the recommendation process once a satisfactory candidate item list has been found.",
    "ToolRec's iterative framework integrates LLMs into recommender systems while enhancing the quality of recommendations.",
    "Contributions.",
    "Our main contributions are as follows:• We propose ToolRec, a framework that deploys LLMs to enhance recommendations via tool learning.",
    "It employs LLMs to closely emulate user preferences, thereby improving the accuracy of recommendations generated during user decision simulation."
  ]
}